# SiteSync Pro — Environment Variables

# All env vars are consumed by the SvelteKit app.
# Copy the app-level example and fill in your values:
#
#   cp apps/sveltekit/.env.example apps/sveltekit/.env.local
#
# Required variables:
#   VITE_CONVEX_URL   — Your Convex deployment URL
#   BETTER_AUTH_SECRET  — Random secret for auth (openssl rand -hex 32)
#   BETTER_AUTH_URL   — Public URL of the app (e.g., http://localhost:3000)
